<td class="textTimeHeader" height="20" valign="top">SUNDAY, DECEMBER 07, 2008 12:37 AM, CST</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="textNormal12">
<div style="overflow: auto;">We feel the love!!!!!!!!  The Cure For Chris benefit this weekend was amazing!!! This was the most beautiful thing anyone could have ever done for Chris!  We love you guys so much&#8230;Chris is so inspired to get better and PUSH through this.  There literally are No words to express how we/he feels.   We just wanted to say thank you to everyone!  Thank you for getting the word out!  Not only does it support Chris but his story could help so many others who face this challenge!  We are truly blown away by all of it and many times we find ourselves speechless and overwhelmed with gratitude.</p>
<p>We can&#8217;t wait to come visit and celebrate his recovery and cure!</p>
<p>Goodnight!</p>
<p>Amy and Chris</p></div>
