<tr>
<td class="textNormal12">
<div style="overflow: auto;">Chris was featured in URB magazine. Go to URB.com and then click on HIVE.  There is a write up about Chris and the benefit that his friends are putting together for him in his home town.  Thank you Beda for getting the word out!!!  WE are so excited about the benefit.  Chris is going to try to video conference in from Houston.</p>
<p>Hope you all are having a great weekend!  We&#8217;re packing and cleaning and getting ready!</p>
<p>Chris&#8217; bag of chemo came out of the pump and spilled all over around 11pm lastnight!  It was a defect in the tube and bag connector.  It really sucked!  Very scary but we got it all worked out.  Chemo freaks me out!</p>
<p>We&#8217;ll keep you posted!!!</p>
<p>Love, Amy</p></div>
