<tr>
<td class="textNormal12">
<div style="overflow: auto;">We have 24 hours to find insurance ( a different policy) otherwise M.D Anderson will kick our paperwork out of the system and we will have to start the process all over again.   We are exhausted with the whole sitation.  But we are not giving up&#8230;anything is possible.</p>
<p>That&#8217;s where we are&#8230;.</p>
<p>Wish I had more to talk about. We are hoping for good news tomorrow.  We have a back up plan&#8230;we&#8217;ll see how things go.</p>
<p>Goodnight!</p>
<p>Amy</p></div>
